Process called "get_localized_strings" that takes locale as Locale returns LocalizedStrings:
    Let language_code be locale["language_code"]
    
    Match language_code:
        When "en":
            Return create_english_strings with locale as locale
        When "fr":
            Return create_french_strings with locale as locale
        When "de":
            Return create_german_strings with locale as locale
        When "es":
            Return create_spanish_strings with locale as locale
        When "ja":
            Return create_japanese_strings with locale as locale
        When "zh":
            Return create_chinese_strings with locale as locale
        When "ar":
            Return create_arabic_strings with locale as locale
        Otherwise:
            Return create_english_strings with locale as locale

